    "description": "<p>OCD Hands Pte. Ltd. was incorporated in 2019. We are NEA-registered Cleaning Business (NEA200314/0049D/N01).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>OCD Hands Pte. Ltd. (UEN 201910049D&nbsp;is a company that provides part-time cleaning services and is licensed by the NEA, which means our clients can depend on both an efficient and well-done service provided by cleaners. The services that we provide are dishwashing and cleaning for both commercial and residential needs. OCD Hands strives to build positive relationships with our clients to ensure communication and to build a good connection with the companies to which we provide our services.</p>\n<p>Additionally, we supply manpower for multiple scenarios including; stewards for &nbsp;events, hotel housekeeping, and public area attendants. In keeping with our &nbsp;cleaning solutions mantra, we are also dedicated to demonstrating efficient and &nbsp;high-quality services which will be in keeping with a client's individual needs and beliefs.</p>",
